    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/8ef46746bc25fd9f176b3a108be477d7.avif?t=1762101454\" width=609 height=303 /></span><br><br>Imagine being confined to your bed by sleep paralysis, unable to move, while something keeps you company in the darkness of your room on a stormy, rainy night. Your only hope is to survive until dawn, using your wits to overcome fear and stay calm. But here comes the real challenge: every blink counts. Can you maintain your sanity and survive until daylight dispels the night terrors?<br><br>Welcome to Bonanit, a 100% random game where no two playthroughs are the same. Each night brings new horrors, and every moment of sleep paralysis tests your mental resilience. The sinister atmosphere intensifies with every whisper in the dark, where each decision could be your last.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/d4e0b5a662768c97547c27bec7c5f2f2.avif?t=1762101454\" width=609 height=195 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/07c25e3e94c2812400c79be29cc7ef62.poster.avif?t=1762101454\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/07c25e3e94c2812400c79be29cc7ef62.webm?t=1762101454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/07c25e3e94c2812400c79be29cc7ef62.mp4?t=1762101454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/4e53045797866c55763a44e52d0ddb57.webp?t=1762101454\" width=526 height=45 /></span><br>In &quot;Bona nit,&quot; experience the paralyzing reality of sleep paralysis. Imagine being trapped in your bed, unable to move, while sensing a sinister presence lurking in the darkness of your room. Every sound, every shadow, and every whisper will make you question your sanity. Can you survive until dawn?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/4e17726f41e6b47b8647aa5be4db56e2.poster.avif?t=1762101454\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/4e17726f41e6b47b8647aa5be4db56e2.webm?t=1762101454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/4e17726f41e6b47b8647aa5be4db56e2.mp4?t=1762101454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/166ac33f657e8cb8a2621b09808bc386.webp?t=1762101454\" width=505 height=45 /></span><br>You will never know what to expect in &quot;Bona nit.&quot; Each game is a unique experience, with randomly generated horrors ensuring that every night is different from the last. This unpredictability keeps you constantly on edge, never knowing what terror awaits around the corner.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/53960025390d833ba8567fc9b14f5a02.poster.avif?t=1762101454\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/53960025390d833ba8567fc9b14f5a02.webm?t=1762101454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/53960025390d833ba8567fc9b14f5a02.mp4?t=1762101454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/59ca6ec0edc1ce578b47a957176a23d9.webp?t=1762101454\" width=505 height=45 /></span><br>&quot;Bona nit&quot; not only tests your survival skills but also your mental strength. Face your worst fears while trying to stay calm in sleep paralysis situations. Every blink and every decision are crucial. Do you have what it takes to keep your sanity amidst the chaos?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/5913feba3a216853330dfc49b9744eab.poster.avif?t=1762101454\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/5913feba3a216853330dfc49b9744eab.webm?t=1762101454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/5913feba3a216853330dfc49b9744eab.mp4?t=1762101454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/bb7ac4fbf4cdca282e358b847e9776d0.webp?t=1762101454\" width=505 height=45 /></span><br>Immerse yourself in a terrifying environment with a raging storm outside and chilling whispers filling the darkness of your room. Sound and shadows combine to create an atmosphere so realistic that you will feel the terror in every fiber of your being. In &quot;Bona nit,&quot; every moment could be your last.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3022010/extras/d8c12436b5970d0527033e246644ea42.poster.avif?t=176210145